item.description:
The Shoreline Family Chiropractice & Wellness invites our Meet Up Group to
Receive a lesson about Natural Health.

Dr. Matt Paterna is our primary Point of Contact.
Please note that we have a new POC.
All members of the staff will assist us during our visit.

When you go in just mention that your are there with Mike's Meet Up
Group. I will determine which of our Meet Up Group(s) that you are in.
I know that some of you are in more than one of my groups.

There will be a chair massage available.

There shall be a lecture in?
Cleanse Detoxification
Maximum Health the Natural Way
and other topics.

If you would like to know more about this office, then please look at

http://www.drpaterna....

www.drpaterna.com

or call them at (203) 932-4476

They are on the West Haven and Milford Boarder
Down by the Shore Line.

They are between the New Alliance Bank and the Baybrook
Post Office.
They are in the Shopping Center that also has Family Dollar.


Mike B
Organizer
item.how_to_find_us: The reception desk can point you out where the Meet Up will be held further in the room.
item.why: Who wants a chair massage, to be cleansed and learn about natural health.
